entries.s_11: I knew from the moment that I saw you! Ah, but this is only the beginning. You must venture forth and complete this undertaking to fulfill your destiny and achieve the rewards that it offers.
entries.s_15: Ah, perhaps not. Perhaps I was mistaken in my initial impression of you. I am disappointed, though fear not...I shall recover my composure in time.
entries.s_16: The victorious Jedi returns! I've heard tales regaling your adventures and must say that I am impressed.
entries.s_20: Look within yourself and discover what you can. It's a fearful adventure, to be sure, but one worthy of taking.
entries.s_22: Greetings, friend. May the Force be with you.
entries.s_24: Greetings, friend. May your journey lead to the destination you seek.
entries.s_6: My friend, how wonderful to see you again. I trust you fare well in your endeavours?
entries.s_7: Come closer, my friend. I have important news for you. For, you see, there are boundless opportunities for those who possess the wisdom to perceive them. Are you one such individual?
